pacman/yaourt:

Use pacman for the official repository, use yaourt for AUR (Arch User Repository)

System update:
pacman -Syu
yaourt -Syua (can be slow, needs to build packages)

Search:
pacman -Ss
yaourt -Ss

Install:
pacman -S
yaourt -S

Remove:
pacman -R
yaourt -R

List:
pacman -Ql

List orphans:
pacman -Qtdq

Remove orphans:
pacman -Rs $(pacman -Qtdq)

Clean:
rm /var/cache/pacman/pkg/*
